Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:01.92,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.92,0:00:02.97,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:04.43,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,It's the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:05.64,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Sticky sea breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.51,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Bright sunshine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:09.19,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Skin-destroying ultraviolet rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.56,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Sexy yukatas at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:14.11,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Donating blood to the mosquitos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.84,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,N-new people to meet, heightened expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:18.58,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Same old faces, different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:20.27,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy food!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:24.33,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Cold noodles after heatstroke, or food poisoning from something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.58,DW,nds,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate summer, or just us?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.09,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,I love them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.97,0:02:15.99,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,This sort of thing is nice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:19.70,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't done anything summer-esque.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:23.28,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,The comic market is pretty summer-esque.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.46,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Not like that, but more under the sun, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.46,0:02:28.91,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.39,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Sora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.17,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,It's the ocean!  Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:35.35,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Alright Kaneru-chan, but take your shoes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:36.71,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow, it's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.49,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Look, there's a sea gull flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.84,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to sit like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.31,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,She's twenty four years old right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.93,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... it's not like we're here to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:43.84,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:45.88,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what'd you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.86,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Drawing camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:55.22,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.49,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,We came all the way to the beach to draw doujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.95,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bright clear sky, just like you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:04.83,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but there's better things you can do under a blue sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.82,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi, you're so perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.82,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what you would call relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.37,0:03:13.83,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,If you have any problems, talk to the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:15.21,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Mastermind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.09,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.79,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay, it's Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.26,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.47,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Justice, are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:25.47,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,No worries, this suit is water-repellent and has excellent air flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.97,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:31.20,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes are crazy too, but why do we have to draw doujin at the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:34.06,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi-san, think of it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:41.57,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,After basking in the sun, we let the stored solar power add an explosive dynamic to our art!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:46.96,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a Power Ranger, but I still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:52.42,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Also, they say that seawater has the same salt concentration as amniotic fluid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:53.60,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.84,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,By placing yourself in a situation similar to your mother's womb,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.35,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,you can add nostalgia to your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.33,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Why would an ero-manga need nostalgia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.56,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm not drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:09.56,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  That's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:10.68,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.62,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Doujinshi spot sale opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:18.07,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty Love-sensei and Nidou Kaneru-sensei's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.33,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Limited edition original art sale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.88,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Najimi-san, our mangas are being advertised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:27.78,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,The sales event starts two days from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.62,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.91,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you advertise it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.30,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  How many of these did you give out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.32,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi-san, I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:41.09,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I've handed out flyers all the way to the next town. Five thousand of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.83,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I hope people show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.71,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,We're going after her, Hoshi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.60,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:05.34,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you two. Just let out the overflowing freedom onto the paper at will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:05.97,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:09.33,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling entrapment more than freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:13.55,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll be able to draw something amazing now that you're cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:16.58,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,With your back to the ocean, there's no place to run or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.58,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I almost want to just throw myself in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.10,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.00,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,A-are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.40,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.47,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I meant Hoshi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.97,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alright... Beside the point,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:36.07,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi-san, that outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:41.56,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be a shame if I couldn't wear it after buying it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:42.23,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.89,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! You look excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.09,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.64,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,But Hoshi-kun, you don't have to work, you should go play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:53.20,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well... Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:56.96,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi-kun is bound to Justice in servitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.45,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm... Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:02.51,Thoughts,h,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we went to the hotel for research...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:05.46,Thoughts,h,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping to make a move if the mood was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.02,Thoughts,h,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, the mood never was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:10.47,Thoughts,h,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2500)}Never was right! Never was right! Never was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:13.18,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I had to open my big mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:18.43,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.25,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Servitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:20.96,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.19,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.31,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:27.30,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:30.11,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,There's alot of customers at noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.95,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,It'll slow down in the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.65,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to work at the seaside shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:37.83,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's play, Najimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.04,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I'm way too pressured by the deadline to play right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.52,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.52,0:06:43.54,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:46.13,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.15,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Sora-chan, come play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.54,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Nidou-san, you don't have time to play either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:54.01,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyuri, will you play with Sora-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.84,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening from the look of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.24,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to thoroughly examine the male figure at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.05,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,You say that way too boldly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:07.35,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,That might actually be beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.75,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave her to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.30,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Come along, Sora-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:11.95,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:16.61,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Um, how about you go to the beach for a sketch too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.16,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll model for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:23.75,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is sharp enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.56,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just go make some yakisoba...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.63,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Nidou-san, aren't you going to swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.63,0:07:36.76,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:40.78,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,B-but I'm vigilantly watching Sora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.84,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,If something were to happen, you can't swim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.51,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,I'll shout for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:47.57,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.89,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Aiorusu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:56.94,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Am I doing a good job as a guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:02.04,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,2500)}No! Aiorusu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.74,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, so relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.69,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Tatami is best for japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:12.15,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,They say ideas come when you change your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.76,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,What a lie.  I can't think of any stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.63,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing, Nidou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.09,DW,x,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:22.60,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Kaneru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.29,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,The bath feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:25.84,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.36,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,So, you guys aren't fighting because you're in the same room, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.31,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.06,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Justice and Hoshi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.05,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,At the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.80,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,At the beach at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.61,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,How bold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:42.63,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd be sleeping here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.09,0:08:46.64,Thoughts,h,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd finally get to sleep in the same room as Najimi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.68,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.97,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed this car from my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:51.88,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.62,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to send him my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:57.84,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Justice-san, you may meet my brother eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.64,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.04,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Him as the brother of the groom and you as a close friend of the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.48,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What makes you so confident about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.59,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Y-youth, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:10.15,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.65,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?  Won't you accept it, already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.31,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I've been suppressing things I shouldn't have to as a healthy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:28.74,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What is youth!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.86,0:09:33.50,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I stayed in there too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.61,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Terrifying is the lure of the hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.71,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Najimi-san, wear this instead of that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:44.31,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think I'll go with the yukata since we're here and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.97,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,M-matching outfits?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.99,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, I got it to show camaraderie for our combined effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.23,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,N-no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:55.69,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,But, I went to the trouble of buying them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.74,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it make you want to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:01.66,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.29,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Najimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:05.11,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to bother us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.29,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a run to the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.95,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,I need every minute I can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:10.78,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:13.55,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,We won't have dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:17.13,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Justice cancelled dinner, saying it's a drawing camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.88,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,That hasty guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.22,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'm not going to die just because I didn't eat tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.56,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,No!  If I don't eat dinner... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.05,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Want some of my snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.27,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.20,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.52,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,We're coming right back after we get food, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.24,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay, food run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.94,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Food run! Food run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:39.53,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow Hoshi-kun's car. We'll go by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.52,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyuri, you can drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:44.45,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:44.82,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:49.25,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, they're both gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:50.93,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.46,DW,s,0000,0000,0000,,Justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:54.48,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.10,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:58.63,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,He was stung by a jellyfish, then partially drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.02,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:02.47,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.04,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.40,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,We were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:16.39,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nidou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:17.88,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.40,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,I-it's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:23.88,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nidou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.66,DW,d,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.66,DW,n,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.39,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to trouble you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.70,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you were the one who saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:35.20,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:39.21,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,You're an important friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.97,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Then, about Najimi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.41,0:11:42.91,DW,j,0000,0000,0000,,That's a seperate matter altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.85,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest in our room for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.81,DW,t,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and can we borrow your car to go to the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:51.68,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.22,DW,h,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
